verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Mine! Mine! Mine!
I know Thou art mine;
Savior, dear Savior,
I know Thou art mine.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Dear Savior, Thou art mine,
How sweet the thought to me;
Let me repeat Thy name,
And lift my heart to Thee.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}My hardened heart was touched;
Thy pard’ning voice I heard;
And joy and peace came in
While list’ning to Thy word.{/lang-eng}
